Unfortunately, we would need authorization from the owner of this account (EMAIL) before we can either move the site into a new account or give you access to edit this site.  They can either reply directly to this ticket, or contact us separately and reference Ticket # {{ticket.id}}

Another option would be to free up the (DOMAIN) domain. This would allow you to use the domain with a new site in a different account. In order to do this, the request would need to come from the person listed as the Registry Contact/owner of the domain: (EMAIL)

Thank you for understanding!
